Definition: SCID in male children resulting from mutation of a gene that codes for a protein on the surface of T cells that allows them to develop a growth factor receptor
Synonyms: X-SCID, severe_combined_immunodeficiency, SCID, in, male, children, resulting, from, mutation, of, a, gene, that, codes, for, protein, on, the, surface, T, cells, allows, them, to, develop, growth, factor, receptor
Category: noun.state
